00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:38,000
 We will have those moments where we fall short.

246
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:44,000
 And how we can be at rest is to know that God isn't changing in that time.

247
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:49,000
 His promise still stands. He still keeps his promise.

248
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:53,000
 And if God could keep his promise to a broken nation

