00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,000
 I'm walking by the promenade.

496
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,000
 It's great.

497
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:51,000
 And I'm getting ready to get into the zone

498
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:53,000
 to read this sermon and really hear from God.

